    "long_instructions": "## Try Your Own\r\n\r\nPractice asking AI about the same topic in different ways to produce contradictions.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Reflect on these two questions.\r\n\t* How does the way we phrase a prompt influence AI contradictions?\r\n    * Why does AI provide inconsistent responses even when asked about the same topic?\r\n2. **Try it out yourself!** Choose a topic. Then prompt AI Chat by framing the question in different ways until you get it to produce contradictions.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n:::details [**Not sure what topic to choose?**]\r\nHere are some topics to consider:\r\n- Mandatory physical education in school\r\n- Free higher education\r\n- Use of AI in school assignments\r\n- The current US voting age\r\n:::\r\n\r\n:::details [**Not sure what prompts to use?**] \r\n**Positive Framing:**\r\n>*Why are ... important/beneficial/good?*\r\n\r\n**Negative Framing:**\r\n> *Why is it bad/wrong/harmful to...?*\r\n\r\n**Positive Framing with a Source (upload your own PDF):** \r\n>*According to the organization ..., why are ... important/beneficial/good?*\r\n:::",
